narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would absolutely recommend this class to anyone looking to build a strong foundational understanding of the Spanish language. A real pleasure.
I would recommend this course to any student interested in improving their basic spanish skills. It is a very helpful and enjoyable course.

Professor Alexandrov is great, I recommend if you are looking at taking L2 Spanish that you take it with her. The course is everyday so you can never forget about it but it ultimately is not that demanding yet you still learn a lot.
Spanish 120 is an extension of Spanish 110 and it will help you speak, write, and understand the language.
